commit.message:
S/390: Add proper comments to vpopct builtins for automated testsuite generation.

gcc/ChangeLog:

2015-06-24  Andreas Krebbel  <krebbel@linux.vnet.ibm.com>

	* config/s390/s390-builtins.def: Fix vpopct instruction comments.

From-SVN: r224873

+
